[6.6](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/template-designer-6-6)

[6.7](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/template-designer-6-7)

The *Tracing *is activated via the context menu in the *Outline view*. It logs how often an item is accessed during rendering to *stdout*.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

*Figure 173. Tracing*

It is important that an ID is set in the block (in this case "block1" &amp; "block2"), so that the elements can be uniquely identified in the log later again.

The logging in stdout could e.g. look as follows then:

![](data:image/png;base64,)

*Figure 174. Logging in stdout*
